== 維護與保養 ==
[[聯合國|聯合國]]藝術委員會（UN Arts Committee）負責聯合國藝術收藏系列的維護<ref name=":0" />。聯合國透過特別授權及規定，由梅塞納斯世界遺產基金會等組織協助保養這些國際文物<ref>{{Cite web|title=Maecenas World Patrimony Foundation: Support|url=http://www.celestialsphere.ch/support.html|accessdate=2007-08-02|author=|date=|format=|publisher=梅塞納斯世界遺產基金會|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706222935/http://www.celestialsphere.ch/support.html|archivedate=2011-07-06}}</ref>；惟其中收藏系列的超過50件作品在過去數十年間均儲存於地庫<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ecpaper.leadersmagazine.cz/2010-issue-1/?page=78-79|title=UN Art – Credits and Captions|author=|date=2010-01|work=Prague Leaders Magazine|publisher=|accessdate=|language=en|format=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110104113220/http://ecpaper.leadersmagazine.cz/2010-issue-1/?page=78-79|archivedate=2011-01-02|last=Ehm|first=Frithjof|pages=78-79}}</ref>。

